[placeholder],

I have need of your services again. At your leisure, return to me in Bree, and I will see that you are informed of what this latest charge entails.

Dawn Appledore
'I am glad that you have returned. I am hopeful that you will be prepared for this latest endeavour.'
You received a letter from your trainer in Bree-town asking for you to return to her. Apparently, there is something that she wishes to teach you.
Deliver the letter to Dawn Appledore in Bree
Dawn Appledore sent you a letter requesting that you visit her in the Bree Jail.\n\nDeliver the letter to Dawn Appledore. She can be found in the Bree Jail.
